Description: ==========
        PingdomLib
        ==========
        
        v0.1.2
        ------
        
        This library exposes the functionality of the pingdom API for usage within
        python. 
        
        
        TODO
        ====
        
        API Calls
        ---------
        
        * Checks (can add, check and modify but not yet delete)
        * Contacts
        * Credits
        * Probes
        * Reference
        * Reports.email
        * Reports.public
        * Reports.shared
        * Results
        * Servertime
        * Settings
        * Summary.average
        * Summary.outage
        * Summary.perforamnce
        * Summary.probes
        * Single
        * Traceroute
        
        Other features
        --------------
        * Gzip Compression, enabled by default
        
